{% block whatWereMyResponsabilites %}
  <h3>What are my responsabilites at Twenga</h3>
  <p>Responsible for the Smart BID product: adjusts the bids inside a {{ link.external("https://ads.google.com", "Google AdWords") }} account in real time, based on the web shop traffic.</p>
  <p>Responsible for the Smart FEED product: allows a shop to push its catalog to {{ link.external("https://shopping.google.com", "Google Shopping") }} and adjusts the bids inside Google Adwords account in real time, based on the web shop traffic.</p>
{% endblock %}

