  <dl>
    <dt>Onboarding process</dt>
    <dd>
      <p>We rewritten the onboarding process for our customers to decrease the time needed for them to be live with our products. This new flow allowed us to decrease the onboarding time by 82.5%.</p>
    </dd>
    <dt>Dashboards</dt>
    <dd>
      <p>We created dashboards for our customers to allowed them to track their performance on <em>Google AdWords</em> and <em>Google Shopping</em>.</p>
    </dd>
    <dt>Performance goals</dt>
    <dd>
      <p>We developed a feature to define the objectives of Cost Of Sale / Return Of Investment for <em>Google AdWords</em> and <em>Google Shopping</em> campaigns on a product level.</p>
    </dd>
    <dt>Billing process</dt>
    <dd>
      <p>Implementation of an automatic process to charge customers, based on their advertising spending: saves time for the accounting team</p>
    </dd>
  </dl>
